$nMPID_エリーゼ|You stand before Elise—master of
secrecy and she who vanishes within
the umbra of the Nohrian dusk...

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Elise was really excited to learn about
Hoshidan customs, so I decided to
tag along on her little adventure.

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Oooh, I bet a shuriken-shaped cake
would be a fun baking challenge...
Wait, no—I need to focus right now!

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|You wanted to know what ninja
training was like, Elise, so no slacking
off. Keep up the pace! Feel that burn!

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Ninja can hold their breath to avoid
detection for....HOW long?! Well, here
goes nothing. Deep breath!

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Hi! I'm Elise, and this is Corrin! We're
friends of $Nf.$k$pWhat's your name? Tell me all
about yourself!

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Hiyah! Refrain from approaching me
carelessly, lest you find yourself on
the pointy end of a shuriken, evildoer!

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|I will see Elise home safely,
no matter what!

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Aww, don't sweat it. I know
you'll get 'em tomorrow!

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Wow, this is gonna be great! Thanks
so much, $Nu!

I'm Corrin, and this is Elise. Hm?
Oh, we're seeing what it's like to
play the part of ninja right now...

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Hey, Big Sis, guess what! We're not
ninja after all! Well, we kinda are,
but...it's complicated, I guess?$k$pTurns out that some ninja are
called "kunoichi!" Isn't that WAY
cooler? Let's be those instead!$k$p$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|"Kunoichi," huh? Now that you
mention it, I think I've heard Kagero
use that term once or twice before...$k$p$nMPID_エリーゼ|Kunoichi are supposed to be super-
sneaky, so we gotta lose all this gear!
Lemme untie this and loosen that...$k$p$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|H-hold on a minute, Elise! You can't
just do that outside of your room!$k$p$nMPID_エリーゼ|WHEW, that sash was tight! We've
gotta get stronger, so let's chow
down like there's no tomorrow!$k$p$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Haha! You're a real handful, Elise, but
I wouldn't have it any other way.
とうっ！
仕留めます！
きゃああっ
いけません…！
やだぁ！
$nMPID_二人|Your life is forfeit!
$nMPID_二人|Time to land... The final blow!
$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Divine punishment!
$nMPID_エリーゼ|Your time is up!
We've been detected...
Corrin's the coolest!
Tear 'em to shreds!
"They're wide open!" "I got this!"
"Ninj-elise!" "Nin...jorrin?"
ふふっ
"That outfit looks good on you, Elise." "*giggle* Thank you! I'm glad you like it."
Umm...
We'll see this through.
Shh! Quiet down...
$nMPID_エリーゼ|Soul-Shredding Shuriken! Hyah!
$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Um, Elise... What are you doing?

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Huh?! Drat, you spotted me... This is
supposed to be my secret training!
$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Why do you need secret training?
$nMPID_エリーゼ|Because the ninja festival is today!

I really need to work on my ninja
skills if I wanna be as strong as Saizo
and Kagero.

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Well, that explains all the shuriken
stuck in the walls...

You never cease to amaze me, Elise.
Your dedication to growing stronger
really knows no bounds!

$nMPID_エリーゼ|I don't need to be the strongest, but I
need to be able to hold my own.

I know I'm kind of the runt of the
litter...

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|That's not true. If you ask me, you're
the strongest of us all.
$nMPID_エリーゼ|You don't mean that!

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Don't I? The reason you train so hard
is to help protect us, right?

That selflessness is what gives you
your strength. I'm proud to call you
my little sister.

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Aw, Corrin... Thank you! You're the
best sister a girl could ask for!

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|I suppose all that's left is to work
on our ninja skills. I bet we could
learn a lot from each other.

$nMPID_エリーゼ|Yeah, let's do it! Concealed
Chameleon Crawl!

$nMPID_比翼カムイ女|Huh?! Where'd you... Heh. You won't
get away that easily... Tracking Tiger
Tackle!
